query:
UPDATE account_move_line
        SET 
            product_id = $1,
            product_uom_id = $2,
            name = $3,
            quantity = $4,
            price_unit = $5,
            discount = $6,
            account_id = $7,
            price_subtotal = $8,
            price_total = $9,
            sequence = COALESCE($10, sequence),
            display_type = $11
        WHERE tenant_id = $12 AND id = $13 AND move_id = $14
